snippet.title: EVOTINCTION | Steam PC | PS5 | Release Date Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
After seven years of development, EVOTINCTION is set to launch on September 13, 2024 on PC and PlayStation 5 simultaneously.

Check it out at:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2005090/EVOTINCTION/
